{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>她在演出當天進行高強度重量訓練，以一張汗流浹背的自拍記錄「Rise and grind（起床就拼）」的日常。現年56歲的她，搭配黑色緊身褲與白色運動鞋入鏡，全程素顏上陣，並將棕色長髮隨性盤起，專注投入有氧與重訓課程。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126156813528469504804923.jpeg/LInpbHgX8hk9XCySpSjjKczjTugmCKPMhpRXqYaUV6k\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><p>點擊查看珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez分享的健身日常：</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126157466476744704478039.jpeg/RaKfYkFaPE69A_bFP1pTmGfhnbduwl4cOnPysTpz8rE\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez分享的汗流浹背的自拍記錄「Rise and grind（起床就拼）」的日常。（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez分享的汗流浹背的自拍記錄「Rise and grind（起床就拼）」的日常。（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126157469354168320673591.jpeg/44X9ZrWP2sk3_SQIpMHnjd8-k3QLjOPVikEZh4pBGYc\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez分享的汗流浹背的自拍記錄「Rise and grind（起床就拼）」的日常。（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez分享的汗流浹背的自拍記錄「Rise and grind（起床就拼）」的日常。（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126157471707303936965728.jpeg/IKJxpeNsSo9d1Qaw40nGKCP2nkKcWu2-RhC640YQuuM\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez分享的汗流浹背的自拍記錄「Rise and grind（起床就拼）」的日常。（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez分享的汗流浹背的自拍記錄「Rise and grind（起床就拼）」的日常。（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126157474026885120967108.jpeg/aw-Nn8QF8-2RIMmIfMxQHr6CZdGwrbXUxs_qf8bP6n8\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez稍早也在同一地點發布另一組照片，並寫下「Keep it simple（保持簡單）」。其中一張照片中，她身穿深紫色運動套裝，坐在健身器材上，緊身瑜伽褲搭配低胸運動內衣與外搭短版罩衫，完美曲線一覽無遺。（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez稍早也在同一地點發布另一組照片，並寫下「Keep it simple（保持簡單）」。其中一張照片中，她身穿深紫色運動套裝，坐在健身器材上，緊身瑜伽褲搭配低胸運動內衣與外搭短版罩衫，完美曲線一覽無遺。（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126157476099002368643208.jpeg/foapqnWk6Zz1UvNQiTGC4hVbXvSz8YsuiM_ylIjP8pQ\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez稍早也在同一地點發布另一組照片，並寫下「Keep it simple（保持簡單）」。其中一張照片中，她身穿深紫色運動套裝，坐在健身器材上，緊身瑜伽褲搭配低胸運動內衣與外搭短版罩衫，完美曲線一覽無遺。（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez稍早也在同一地點發布另一組照片，並寫下「Keep it simple（保持簡單）」。其中一張照片中，她身穿深紫色運動套裝，坐在健身器材上，緊身瑜伽褲搭配低胸運動內衣與外搭短版罩衫，完美曲線一覽無遺。（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126157460889931776519743.jpeg/Sf4mus2WWQAMhFybIq5ZaytSoaEPNIpBTZB8Mk2QfDI\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez稍早也在同一地點發布另一組照片，並寫下「Keep it simple（保持簡單）」。其中一張照片中，她身穿深紫色運動套裝，坐在健身器材上，緊身瑜伽褲搭配低胸運動內衣與外搭短版罩衫，完美曲線一覽無遺。（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez稍早也在同一地點發布另一組照片，並寫下「Keep it simple（保持簡單）」。其中一張照片中，她身穿深紫色運動套裝，坐在健身器材上，緊身瑜伽褲搭配低胸運動內衣與外搭短版罩衫，完美曲線一覽無遺。（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><p>從畫面中可見，珍妮花在健身房內對著鏡頭自拍，背後擺滿各式重量訓練器材，並以簡單一句「Rise and grind」為照片下註解。向來熱愛運動的她，近期也分享多張健身照，展現自律生活。</p><p>她稍早也在同一地點發布另一組照片，並寫下「Keep it simple（保持簡單）」。其中一張照片中，她身穿深紫色運動套裝，坐在健身器材上，緊身瑜伽褲搭配低胸運動內衣與外搭短版罩衫，完美曲線一覽無遺。</p><p>點擊珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez的相片：</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126158697056178176531869.jpeg/N_erTyrBpL81kandJDbz_hN_PdDDwWqexCqRC8QqkQs\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126158699648389120081394.jpeg/49QVfnekk81RtyCAaYGpMNwsrVZN_607WgtEuloLRLo\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126158702190268416601328.jpeg/N9L1QJrDyLi7f8kQsjFsYZlQfCmbR4WdFysSQhcrEkI\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126158704765702144379015.jpeg/frw-x_R3gdMAJAQowt0NJCpPNAeanCVm7l30me5d9Jk\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126158707496325120058461.jpeg/YudC_i7jS3yXTllWgipQTpC_HGvmCK6Nqx_AE6sfwBM\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126158702965952512016387.jpeg/dpjWlLexq22c04iqOUCiWgOii4Y8T5KMMF3kIDBd5CA\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126158705285533696612708.jpeg/tqjHZfs3ybl6u-J99GQmS_7bVp1lWO0difXlr4n15a8\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126158708125208576207691.jpeg/pts-QJJixD5N-QKnwgclY55Kgjd4bIwfQD5n2kA-Z9o\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126158710528675840562390.jpeg/2RasOApGL_nG6cMvtiDAJtUFPnyhlV0EME4BizBOAYs\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126158712718233600524180.jpeg/zR_E_FhjeoV03zY9_1UQNzPb7VQQyg5AAgW4xAIFuMQ\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126158703410548736204839.jpeg/i6MGTCiUGuA2rhhUF0oO_rCzdmqhuPkQQHTr7UB06-0\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126158706116005888143279.jpeg/-6Kx81uqwswDOV9maBgX5ebqZkRspRrXZ7MzaGezM2g\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126158708838240256570342.jpeg/am_D09koFEIym7DbPiq-Fd8czA4oACSmjPJgA4zyYAM\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126158710998437888428371.jpeg/GkuEd1LyM3B7Sf2wK8gUxqFIQmOUJP8XwDOZ48AzmeM\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126158713401905152096852.jpeg/Z2ohbKBTP1wOmjPeH9DNDnokk5sJOd136A9cm-gPXJs\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126158703230193664905132.jpeg/CrHszH4qLhzypDRXdhNIgbOdLOpN5BF7Vfzu9FX87vQ\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126158705721741312697201.jpeg/lvdxU9F_Xv35EPbUgY4WebL5dQadoE7wEymXHxMplx8\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126158708448169984276390.jpeg/mEr1MhGbBCfcYJOtoNbdhdW3WPFARs4jAgB7RAIAe0Q\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126158710843248640458109.jpeg/zmz6h-9fdQ5c8bHS_Huh-Hyw6SyJeAVOoHbL5qB2y-Y\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126158713305436160620795.jpeg/x2lDhoFBW1LJTg5oH5m0LKr-azt9mxRaU24QTVNuEE0\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126158694174691328360219.jpeg/vZH0woopQ6KPGIscjuktCIcE4qkJDnalZ9fqmWfX6pk\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126158696724959232781423.jpeg/yi5X39G495wHaC-8Qfw8Cil-Vp-4ANDjEBbVKhAW1So\" alt=\"珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）\"><figcaption>珍妮花露柏絲Jennifer Lopez（Instagram@jlo）</figcaption></figure><p>另一張圖片則引用勵志語錄：「目標很簡單，比昨天更好，每一天。」接續的照片中，她再度坐在器材上擺拍，大方展現自信姿態；最後一張則側身做出弓箭步動作，展現結實線條。貼文曝光後，粉絲紛紛湧入留言大讚，有人直呼「女王狀態太好了」，也有人驚嘆她的凍齡身材。</p><p>她早在2025年5月就宣布重返「賭城」，這也是她繼2016年至2018年在好萊塢星球Zappos劇院推出《All I Have》駐唱後，再度於拉斯維加斯長期演出。此次新駐唱場地選在凱薩宮的The Colosseum劇院，並於去年12月30日正式開跑，隨後於3月多個周末持續登台。此外，珍妮花近期也傳出受邀赴印度婚禮演出，據悉酬勞高達140萬英鎊（約1482萬港元），再度展現其國際巨星的吸金實力。</p><p>延伸閱讀：Justin Timberlake曾被爆醉駕、偷食　妻忍無可忍14年婚姻亮紅燈</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210202/433251224662315008319087.jpeg/u7qyxg4I_1WsPb2YCIhclN-La6DP-KmxeDmWnHg5lpw\" alt=\"【延伸閱讀：Justin Timberlake曾被爆醉駕、偷食　妻忍無可忍14年婚姻亮紅燈】Justin Timberlake與老婆Jessica Biel的14年婚姻亮紅燈。（GettyImages）\"><figcaption>【延伸閱讀：Justin Timberlake曾被爆醉駕、偷食　妻忍無可忍14年婚姻亮紅燈】Justin Timberlake與老婆Jessica Biel的14年婚姻亮紅燈。（GettyImages）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260428/1125816897036619776958642.jpeg/ijcKnsNss188YBXbLjEhYfDomNqXewBc2b9Cwtm_QsI\" alt=\"Justin Timberlake與老婆Jessica Biel（Getty Images）\"><figcaption>Justin Timberlake與老婆Jessica Biel（Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3679400/org/7adad1cc093ce759b8af4c322bc737c1.jpg/MeOmcMaerQKvTxAL_YvF8QjWtvspXvaVcWOumHFjrpg\" alt=\"Justin Timberlake結婚後一直以愛妻形象示人。（justintimberlake@IG）\"><figcaption>Justin Timberlake結婚後一直以愛妻形象示人。（justintimberlake@IG）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3679397/org/adffff75066ccad312e72d89be0799ee.jpg/wsmre7YQg9RfrDGo4zWuh2mM0bltsaQjpwL1zqcC9c4\" alt=\"Justin Timberlake不時在IG上曬與愛妻親密合照。（justintimberlake@IG）\"><figcaption>Justin Timberlake不時在IG上曬與愛妻親密合照。（justintimberlake@IG）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210202/433251226726043648205618.jpeg/ViKBzp6-j6_soJfTTLCIWfxAvmAqEQAbfE1FtnxNRbY\" alt=\"Justin Timberlake與老婆Jessica Biel（IG@jessicabiel）\"><figcaption>Justin Timberlake與老婆Jessica Biel（IG@jessicabiel）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20231021/792434441422245888361078.jpeg/qd_uIV81L2Z_AzhmeU0kh0bg1_AgjNMGrpLjfa6S430\" alt=\"Justin Timberlake與Jessica Biel疑因Justin的違規行為生變。（GettyImages）\"><figcaption>Justin Timberlake與Jessica Biel疑因Justin的違規行為生變。（GettyImages）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/192975/org/1bddebbfe9637bbd8cecb75f04e44f6a.jpg/v-B9LvUT-isHEHJzA1sws-zeY7hR8WWwrH2xQ6x9sUM\" alt=\"Justin Timberlake與老婆Jessica Biel（Getty Images）\"><figcaption>Justin Timberlake與老婆Jessica Biel（Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20250801/1027905078692286464716390.png/CXnIeqHQLDkLPFeyvL158LoZk6qBdaMZpGfLxKRny8Q\" alt=\"Justin Timberlake（IG@justintimberlake）\"><figcaption>Justin Timberlake（IG@justintimberlake）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/977361/org/807935ce0b4d3172c51ca8afc443e34c.jpg/mf-wIM8ytMK5Xuzem_q0Ft_-lxn2-KvSCPTItwj0yLc\" alt=\"jessica biel (jessicabiel instagram)\"><figcaption>jessica biel (jessicabiel instagram)</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20250801/1027905076079104000063741.png/Y5vQ3Mrk8G8HaUb3zXjRFF78IGVK7wAP6Q15sekNebE\" alt=\"Justin Timberlake（IG@justintimberlake）\"><figcaption>Justin Timberlake（IG@justintimberlake）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20220719/626044105037844480310425.jpeg/I-oHQJdjuttlednlwnSP6XBigDgK2LHiVV0fX1VdH18\" alt=\"Justin Timberlake（Getty Images）\"><figcaption>Justin Timberlake（Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>延伸閱讀：</p><p>王俐人轉戰SWAG能紅多久？命理師說出殘酷真相</p><p>迪麗熱巴驚傳身體出狀況！直播數度輕壓腹部 強忍不適</p><p>【本文獲「聯合新聞網」授權轉載。】</p></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-29T16:10:11.594923+00:00","quality":{"score":3,"chars":2816,"images":40,"source":"HK01 娛樂","fallback":"none"}}